<blockquote>
  <p><a href="#_Toc473714774">Offshore processing<br>
  </a><a href="#_Toc473714775">Boat turnbacks<br>
  </a><a href="#_Toc473714776">Mandatory immigration detention<br>
  </a><a href="#_Toc473714777">Regional cooperation, border
  protection and anti-people smuggling</a></p>
</blockquote>

