<blockquote>
  <p><a href="#_Toc473714779">Temporary not permanent protection<br>
  </a><a href="#_Toc473714780">Australia&rsquo;s Humanitarian Program.</a></p>
</blockquote>

<p><a href="#_Toc473714781">What are the alternatives?</a></p>

